Interface Measure

All Known Subinterfaces:

public interface Measure
extends AbstractMeasureElement

A representation of the model object 'Measure'.

The following features are supported:

  • Category

  • Scope
  • Measure Label Format
  • Refinement To
  • Refinement From
  • Equivalent To
  • Equivalent From
  • Recursive To

  • Visible
  • Measure Relationships
